# .graphifyignore — controls what graphify indexes for 42-Command-Center.
# Syntax is gitignore-compatible. Keeps the graph focused on real source code.

# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/

# --- Build / generated artifacts ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Lock files (huge, no structural value) ---
**/*.lock
**/bun.lock
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/uv.lock

# --- Minified / generated ---
**/*.min.js
**/*.min.css
**/*.map

# --- Binary / media ---
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.webp
**/*.ico
**/*.svg
**/*.pdf
**/*.mp4
**/*.woff
**/*.woff2
**/*.ttf
**/*.eot

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Download / perf data ---
download/
perf/
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3

# --- The graphify output itself (don't graph the graph) ---
graphify-out/

# --- Git ---
.git/

# --- Large generated reports ---
worklog.md
PLATFORM-REPORT.md
